00:53:37.505 --> 00:53:38.882
<font color="white">Of course. I believe you.</font><font color="white"></font>

827
00:53:38.965 --> 00:53:41.134
<font color="white">Then why do I have to transfer?</font><font color="white"></font>

828
00:53:41.217 --> 00:53:42.886
<font color="white">I didn't do anything wrong.</font><font color="white"></font>

829
00:53:45.639 --> 00:53:47.891
<font color="white">Why did you have to grovel and kneel?</font><font color="white"></font>

830
00:53:48.475 --> 00:53:50.518
<font color="white">Is it because Hye-ri's dad</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">is a powerful man?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

831
00:53:51.269 --> 00:53:52.854
<font color="white">I'm so ashamed.</font><font color="white"></font>

832
00:53:53.855 --> 00:53:56.733
<font color="white">I feel so angry. frustrated. and pathetic.</font><font color="white"></font>

833
00:53:57.817 --> 00:53:59.569
<font color="white">What have you done with your life?</font><font color="white"></font>

834
00:54:01.196 --> 00:54:03.782
<font color="white">Her dad's a rich chairman</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">with lots of connections.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

835
00:54:04.574 --> 00:54:07.202
<font color="white">but why are you a lowly office worker?</font><font color="white"></font>

836
00:54:08.411 --> 00:54:10.121
<font color="white">Why did you even have me?</font><font color="white"></font>

837
00:54:11.998 --> 00:54:12.832
<font color="white">Min-ji.</font><font color="white"></font>

838
00:54:12.916 --> 00:54:13.959
<font color="white">As my dad…</font><font color="white"></font>

839
00:54:16.002 --> 00:54:17.170
<font color="white">As my dad…</font><font color="white"></font>

840
00:54:24.010 --> 00:54:26.680
<font color="white">As my dad. you mean the world to me.</font><font color="white"></font>

841
00:54:27.639 --> 00:54:28.932
<font color="white">I don't have a mom.</font><font color="white"></font>

842
00:54:29.516 --> 00:54:31.101
<font color="white">You're all I have left.</font><font color="white"></font>

843
00:54:32.310 --> 00:54:34.062
<font color="white">but if you're not on my side…</font><font color="white"></font>

844
00:54:34.145 --> 00:54:36.147
<font color="white">They're the bad ones.</font><font color="white"></font>

845
00:54:36.773 --> 00:54:39.651
<font color="white">You. of all people. should've believed me.</font><font color="white"></font>

846
00:54:44.656 --> 00:54:45.573
<font color="white">Let's go home.</font><font color="white"></font>

847
00:54:45.657 --> 00:54:47.158
<font color="white">I don't want to be with you.</font><font color="white"></font>

848
00:54:47.742 --> 00:54:49.786
<font color="white">I'm staying at Hye-ryeong's tonight.</font><font color="white"></font>

849
00:54:49.869 --> 00:54:51.162
<font color="white">so don't call me.</font><font color="white"></font>

850
00:54:51.246 --> 00:54:52.747
<font color="white">If you do.</font><font color="white"></font>

851
00:54:53.957 --> 00:54:55.709
<font color="white">I'll run away from home.</font><font color="white"></font>

852
00:54:57.669 --> 00:54:58.586
<font color="white">Min-ji.</font><font color="white"></font>

853
00:55:00.422 --> 00:55:02.007
<font color="white">It's your birthday tomorrow.</font><font color="white"></font>

854
00:55:02.841 --> 00:55:03.675
<font color="white">Kim Min-ji!</font><font color="white"></font>

855
00:55:11.307 --> 00:55:13.226
<font color="white">I hate my birthday.</font><font color="white"></font>

856
00:55:16.813 --> 00:55:18.481
<font color="white">It's the day Mom died.</font><font color="white"></font>

857
00:55:52.057 --> 00:55:53.308
{\an8}<font color="white">THE LATE IM YU-JIN</font><font color="white"></font>

858
00:56:15.038 --> 00:56:17.082
<font color="white">These flowers are my favorite.</font><font color="white"></font>

859
00:56:17.665 --> 00:56:18.875
<font color="white">They're called honeysuckles.</font><font color="white"></font>

860
00:56:19.375 --> 00:56:20.919
<font color="white">The meaning behind them is pretty too.</font><font color="white"></font>

861
00:56:21.961 --> 00:56:23.088
<font color="white">Do you know what it is?</font><font color="white"></font>

862
00:56:23.671 --> 00:56:24.506
<font color="white">What is it?</font><font color="white"></font>

863
00:56:25.173 --> 00:56:26.007
<font color="white">Love and…</font><font color="white"></font>

864
00:56:26.841 --> 00:56:27.801
<font color="white">-</font><font color="white"><font color="white"><i>devotion.</i></font></font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Devotion.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

865
00:56:33.848 --> 00:56:36.392
<font color="white">I'm sorry. Yu-jin.</font><font color="white"></font>

866
00:57:40.582 --> 00:57:42.125
<font color="white"><i>I have something to tell you.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

867
00:57:42.208 --> 00:57:44.169
<font color="white"><i>I'll be at the back gate at school.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

868
00:57:44.252 --> 00:57:45.712
<font color="white"><i>I'll wait until you get here.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

869
00:58:28.588 --> 00:58:31.925
<font color="white">DAD</font><font color="white"></font>

870
00:58:33.885 --> 00:58:36.846
<font color="white"><i>The person you are trying to reach</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>is unavailable. You will be redirected…</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

871
00:58:37.889 --> 00:58:39.599
<font color="white"><i>I don't want to be with you.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

872
00:58:40.308 --> 00:58:42.435
<font color="white">I'm staying at Hye-ryeong's tonight.</font><font color="white"></font>

873
00:58:42.519 --> 00:58:43.811
<font color="white">so don't call me.</font><font color="white"></font>

874
00:58:45.188 --> 00:58:46.356
<font color="white">If you do.</font><font color="white"></font>

875
00:58:47.565 --> 00:58:49.150
<font color="white">I'll run away from home.</font><font color="white"></font>

876
00:59:18.012 --> 00:59:21.766
