891
01:00:36.090 --> 01:00:37.300
<font color="white">Have you seen her?</font><font color="white"></font>

892
01:00:40.720 --> 01:00:43.264
<font color="white">No. she hasn't come to school yet.</font><font color="white"></font>

893
01:00:52.940 --> 01:00:54.108
<font color="white">Kim Nam-hoon?</font><font color="white"></font>

894
01:00:55.109 --> 01:00:57.612
<font color="white">Did you meet Min-ji yesterday?</font><font color="white"></font>

895
01:00:59.280 --> 01:01:02.241
<font color="white">I didn't send her that DM.</font><font color="white"></font>

896
01:01:02.867 --> 01:01:04.327
<font color="white">hey were these thugs…</font><font color="white"></font>

897
01:01:05.453 --> 01:01:07.455
<font color="white"><i>I only heard something</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>about the back gate.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

898
01:01:08.373 --> 01:01:09.499
<font color="white"><i>I'm sorry.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

899
01:01:10.416 --> 01:01:12.543
<font color="white"><i>I couldn't do anything</i></font><font color="white"></font>

900
01:01:12.627 --> 01:01:14.003
<font color="white"><i>because they took my phone.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

901
01:02:24.282 --> 01:02:27.827
<font color="white"><i>How on earth did you raise your child</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>for her to act this way?</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

902
01:03:04.572 --> 01:03:06.491
<font color="white">We just have to act like</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">we don't know anything.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

903
01:03:06.574 --> 01:03:08.618
<font color="white">I told everyone to keep quiet.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">so don't worry.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

904
01:03:08.701 --> 01:03:11.245
<font color="white">-But you never know.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Just trust me.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

905
01:03:11.329 --> 01:03:12.997
<font color="white">You know I'm not some low-life thug.</font><font color="white"></font>

906
01:03:14.957 --> 01:03:16.501
<font color="white">Hey. it's all clean now.</font><font color="white"></font>

907
01:03:17.084 --> 01:03:19.128
