909
01:03:23.132 --> 01:03:24.217
<font color="white">Nobody will find her.</font><font color="white"></font>

910
01:03:24.300 --> 01:03:26.093
<font color="white">And you said her dad's a loser. right?</font><font color="white"></font>

911
01:03:27.094 --> 01:03:29.806
<font color="white">-Can I ask a question?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Damn it. you scared me!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

912
01:03:30.348 --> 01:03:32.809
<font color="white">I'm Min-ji's dad.</font><font color="white"></font>

913
01:03:33.935 --> 01:03:36.187
<font color="white">We don't know where she is.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">so just go on your way.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

914
01:03:37.271 --> 01:03:39.440
<font color="white">I never said I was looking for her.</font><font color="white"></font>

915
01:03:44.612 --> 01:03:47.406
<font color="white">This is your hair tie. right?</font><font color="white"></font>

916
01:03:47.490 --> 01:03:48.449
<font color="white">It was on the ground.</font><font color="white"></font>

917
01:03:52.787 --> 01:03:56.457
<font color="white">I said go on your way</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">unless you want your ass kicked!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

918
01:03:56.541 --> 01:03:58.793
<font color="white">-It's yours. right?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Goddamn it.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

919
01:04:08.845 --> 01:04:09.971
<font color="white">Look at you.</font><font color="white"></font>

920
01:04:11.180 --> 01:04:13.558
<font color="white">-You're dead meat.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-I'll ask you one last time.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

921
01:04:14.976 --> 01:04:16.644
<font color="white">-Where's Min-ji?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Hey. old man.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

922
01:04:16.727 --> 01:04:17.854
<font color="white">What do you think?</font><font color="white"></font>

923
01:04:18.437 --> 01:04:19.313
<font color="white">Huh?</font><font color="white"></font>

924
01:04:19.397 --> 01:04:21.148
<font color="white">Is it clocking to you that you're screwed?</font><font color="white"></font>

925
01:04:25.361 --> 01:04:28.030
<font color="white">Who the hell do you think you are?</font><font color="white"></font>

926
01:04:28.114 --> 01:04:29.073
<font color="white">You think you're special?</font><font color="white"></font>

927
01:04:29.156 --> 01:04:31.951
<font color="white">Show me. then.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">Take off your clothes and fight.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

928
01:04:32.034 --> 01:04:33.703
