929
01:04:35.913 --> 01:04:36.914
<font color="white"><i>Let me go!</i></font><font color="white"></font>

930
01:04:37.790 --> 01:04:39.458
<font color="white">Put down the gun.</font><font color="white"></font>

931
01:04:40.167 --> 01:04:41.669
<font color="white">Let me go.</font><font color="white"></font>

932
01:04:42.795 --> 01:04:44.714
<font color="white">Discharge me right now!</font><font color="white"></font>

933
01:04:50.928 --> 01:04:51.846
<font color="white"><i>You can't discharge him.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

934
01:04:51.929 --> 01:04:53.556
<font color="white">You know as well as I do. sir.</font><font color="white"></font>

935
01:04:53.639 --> 01:04:56.475
<font color="white">No one can ever know he exists.</font><font color="white"></font>

936
01:04:56.559 --> 01:04:58.352
<font color="white"><i>Codename 66.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

937
01:04:58.436 --> 01:04:59.854
<font color="white"><i>A North Korean operative who defected</i></font><font color="white"></font>

938
01:04:59.937 --> 01:05:01.814
<font color="white"><i>and was recruited</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>by South Korean intelligence.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

939
