<font color="white"><i>on five occasions</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

940
01:05:03.649 --> 01:05:05.610
<font color="white"><i>and has been credited with</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>17 infiltration missions in the North.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

941
01:05:05.693 --> 01:05:09.071
<font color="white"><i>He led the assassination operation</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>targeting North Korea's supreme commander.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

942
01:05:09.155 --> 01:05:12.325
