<font color="white"><i>to assign teams to track him.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

943
01:05:14.243 --> 01:05:15.119
<font color="white">What the hell?</font><font color="white"></font>

944
01:05:36.432 --> 01:05:38.768
<font color="white"><i>Discharging someone like him</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>is unthinkable.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

945
01:05:38.851 --> 01:05:41.646
<font color="white">If the North finds out he's still alive.</font><font color="white"></font>

946
01:05:41.729 --> 01:05:43.356
<font color="white">his existence alone…</font><font color="white"></font>

947
01:05:44.440 --> 01:05:45.858
