948
01:05:52.782 --> 01:05:53.991
<font color="white">Tell me.</font><font color="white"></font>

949
01:05:55.576 --> 01:05:56.577
<font color="white">Where's Min-ji?</font><font color="white"></font>

950
01:06:37.868 --> 01:06:41.497
<font color="white">AGENT KIM REACTIVATED</font><font color="white"></font>

951
01:06:42.248 --> 01:06:43.624
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>-The law?</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>-Who the hell are you?</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

952
01:06:44.834 --> 01:06:45.668
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>I guess…</i></font><font color="white"></font>

953
01:06:48.671 --> 01:06:50.339
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>I'll just be a middle-aged outlaw.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

954
01:06:50.923 --> 01:06:53.342
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>The government denies</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>Agent Kim's existence.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

955
01:06:53.426 --> 01:06:54.552
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Arm the infiltration team.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

956
01:06:55.803 --> 01:06:56.846
{\an8}<font color="white">Hey. mister!</font><font color="white"></font>

957
01:06:58.055 --> 01:07:00.266
{\an8}<font color="white">Is that bastard sleeping right now?</font><font color="white"></font>

958
01:07:00.349 --> 01:07:01.517
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>In this situation?</i></font><font color="white"></font>

959
01:07:02.059 --> 01:07:04.437
{\an8}<font color="white">I'm only keeping you alive</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">because I believe my daughter is.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

960
01:07:07.148 --> 01:07:08.941
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>-Daddy!</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>-Is that you. Min-ji?</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

961
01:07:10.818 --> 01:07:12.319
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>I took care of the girl's body.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

